
Overview of noun absurdity

The noun absurdity has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (6) absurdity, absurdness, ridiculousness -- (a message whose content is at variance with reason)
2. (1) absurdity, fatuity, fatuousness, silliness -- (a ludicrous folly; "the crowd laughed at the absurdity of the clown's behavior")
